being transferred this time.
\N<Zuuteruka>You understand... It's someone you know very well.

\N<Segi>Th-this... voice... could it be...?
\N<Segi>...Zeda...
white

When I think about it... I might still be living in the
past. Maybe I'm still bound by it.
As if to prove it, I've encountered that man again.

I have no regrets about risking my life to protect my
family... the things that are important to me.

I'm not ashamed. There's no reason for me to be. I just did
what I could at that time.
However... even so.

The anger and resentment towards the men who trampled over
me... those negative emotions don't disappear.
They can't disappear. They shouldn't be able to.

That applies to Zuuteruka in front of me now... and to that
man as well.

I am... My heart is surely living in the past while looking
towards the future.
